INSERT INTO `faqs` VALUES (1,'How do you determine the budget for an interior design project?','At our interior design company, we assess various factors such as project scope, client preferences, and desired quality to determine an appropriate budget. We also consider any specific materials, furnishings, or customizations requested by the client. Our goal is to provide a comprehensive estimate that aligns with the client\'s vision and financial resources.','2023-06-28 05:13:40','2023-06-28 05:13:40'),(2,'Can you work with existing furniture and decor, or do you recommend starting from scratch?','We can definitely work with existing furniture and decor if you wish to incorporate them into the design. Our interior design team will assess the condition, style, and functionality of your existing items to determine if they can be integrated seamlessly into the overall design plan. If needed, we can also recommend complementary pieces to enhance your existing collection.','2023-06-28 05:13:40','2023-06-28 05:13:40'),(3,'How involved will I be in the decision-making process throughout the project?','We highly value our clients\' input and collaboration throughout the interior design process. Your involvement can vary based on your preferences and availability. We will schedule regular meetings and consultations to discuss design concepts, material selections, color schemes, and any other decisions that require your input. Our aim is to ensure that the final design reflects your personal style and preferences.','2023-06-28 05:13:40','2023-06-28 05:13:40'),(4,'Can you provide examples of your previous work and client references?','Absolutely! We are proud of our portfolio and would be happy to showcase our previous interior design projects. We can provide you with a collection of photographs, renderings, or even arrange for site visits to completed projects, subject to client consent. Additionally, we can provide you with contact information for previous clients who have agreed to serve as references, so you can gain insights into their experience working with us.','2023-06-28 05:13:40','2023-06-28 05:13:40'),(5,'What is your approach to sustainable and eco-friendly design practices?','At our interior design company, we prioritize sustainability and eco-friendly design practices. We strive to incorporate environmentally responsible materials, energy-efficient solutions, and sustainable design principles into our projects. We can recommend eco-friendly options for furniture, flooring, lighting, and other elements of the design. Our team aims to create spaces that are not only aesthetically pleasing but also contribute to a healthier environment.','2023-06-28 05:13:40','2023-06-28 05:13:40');
